---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const title = "プロジェクト1（タイトル）";
---
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{title} | Cooper Lender</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: system-ui; max-width: 900px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 16px;">
    <header style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;">
      <a href={`${base}ja/`}>&larr; 戻る</a>
      <nav>
        <a href={`${base}en/`} style="margin-right:12px;">EN</a>
        <a href={`${base}ja/`}>日本語</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <h1 style="margin-top:24px;">{title}</h1>
    <p><strong>一言説明：</strong> 何を作ったか＋なぜ重要か。</p>

    <h2>概要</h2>
